title: Looking for developers for a learning + social media app
description:
Our team is building a real-time running log and course sharing platform.

We're looking forward to hearing from all you running and tech lovers out there!

Our goal is to finish the MVP in 2 months and launch it on the store to get live users and maintain it! (We have plans to add additional features even after it's on the store).

We don't have a specific tech stack for the frontend - we'll work with your tech stack, whether it's IOS, Android, or cross-platform.

We are looking for people who are passionate about learning and building a portfolio together ‼
